About Blockchain.com

Founded in 2011, Blockchain.com has built one of the leading brands in the crypto industry by offering secure, reliable services to customers in over 200 countries. Venture backed since 2014, Blockchain.com has raised $537M of equity, valued at $5.2B. Both the Consumer and Institutional businesses are highly profitable with $1.5T+ transacted and ⅓ of all BTC transactions through our retail platform since inception.
